{"tid":2366335,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男生與工人涉藏噴漆白電油受審 拘捕警坦承不知被告做過甚麼","createTime":"2021-01-14T11:57:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T12:31:17.000Z","uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"64c6d9ff542e8f6c6c6a9cf97d996695bd5c5460","tid":2366335,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T11:57:11.000Z","msg":"民陣前年12月1日發起「毋忘初心大遊行」，雖然事前獲發不反對通知書，但途中警方在尖沙嘴一帶驅散群眾，其中兩男涉嫌管有噴漆及白電油等被捕。他們否認管有物品意圖摧毀財產等罪，案件今開審。有警員供稱，當時約有百名市民包圍半百警察，他因看到速龍警突然衝前，遂上前幫助同袍制服被告。不過，作供警員坦承當時看不到被告做了甚麼動作，亦沒有搜查被告背包。辯方指，從現場市民角度來看，當時應是警員將他們包圍，警員對此不同意。<br />\n<br />\n警稱不知當日活動有否不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n裁判官<span class=\"red\">葉啓亮</span>問，鄧稱第一眼見到首被告時，對方是面向他，那麼他怎能肯定檢獲的背囊屬於首被告？鄧回應指，當首被告面向他時，他可以看到其背囊的肩帶；被告轉身逃跑後，他便看到背囊的模樣。鄧指，從他看見至制服首被告，<span class=\"red\">其視線從沒離開首被告</span>，兩人之間亦沒有阻隔。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">警員周天威</span>將首被告帶返警署後，才在其黑背囊內搜出涉案黑色噴漆、藍色帽、縮骨傘、口罩、生理鹽水、黑色長袖上衣等物。他表示，<span class=\"red\">首被告在案發現場或帶返警署後皆沒有戴手套，他不知為何首被告在警署拍攝的照片中戴了手套。</span>"},{"pid":"51dde0ec0c40bf007c6598a1ee41eb8e694cf151","tid":2366335,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T11:57:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210114/IJ6YEBHG3JA4JDIBOS577IVABE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210114%2FIJ6YEBHG3JA4JDIBOS577IVABE%2F&d=qXcR1A%2FTALq%2FhnoNE0cJVeDrFCZ%2FFQqiuLijmhCLlc8%3D&h=0d07948a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210114%2FIJ6YEBHG3JA4JDIBOS577IVABE%2F&h=11e0f87b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210114/IJ6YEBHG3JA4JDIBOS577IVABE/</a>"},{"pid":"956cc757daee5e811db783c5eb414fa5f86e6eb5","tid":2366335,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T11:57:54.000Z","msg":"本案首被告裝修工人林**（22歲）被指當日在尖沙嘴梳士巴利花園外管有一支噴漆，次被告男學生黃**（23歲）則被指管有兩罐白電油及一個打火機，兩人各被控管有物品意圖摧毀財產罪。黃另被控管有適合作非法用途工具罪，涉及一包索帶。"},{"pid":"22cecf32db6473c9603645c9e372792b271b8536","tid":2366335,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T11:57:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"762f469f99b295defb1bb820da03982fb09946eb","tid":2366335,"uid":57205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T11:59:00.000Z","msg":"放心，紅官會FF點犯罪去重判"},{"pid":"f61144bbbe4db750a28348b4ae7472d696e75f92","tid":2366335,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eca182630b6227d48def10eb76d666023c75094","tid":2366335,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:03:33.000Z","msg":"林手足應該有得打證物, 黃手足就幾危.."},{"pid":"b84f7e883365a23a5343db81efbfe782c4055311","tid":2366335,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:16:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0a6d0d9c0766718a7066a62c03dbeab5c8b3ba6","tid":2366335,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:31:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}